list_cmd: if (dbtype = 'ORACLE') { [select alloc_rule_hdr.*, alloc_rule_hdr.rowid from alloc_rule_hdr where not exists (select 'x' from ord_line ol where ol.rule_nam = alloc_rule_hdr.rule_nam and ol.wh_id = alloc_rule_hdr.wh_id) and ins_dt < sysdate - /*=moca_util.days(*/ 40 /*=)*/ and rownum < 50001] } else {[select alloc_rule_hdr.* from alloc_rule_hdr where not exists (select 'x' from ord_line ol where ol.rule_nam = alloc_rule_hdr.rule_nam and ol.wh_id = alloc_rule_hdr.wh_id) and ins_dt < sysdate - /*=moca_util.days(*/ 40 /*=)*/ and rownum < 50001] }

if (dbtype = 'ORACLE') { [select * from cnthdr where adddte < sysdate - /*=moca_util.days(*/ 40 /*=)*/ and not exists (select 'x' from cntwrk where cnthdr.cntbat = cntwrk.cntbat and cntwrk.cntsts not in ('C', 'N')) and rownum<1000] } else { [select * from cnthdr where adddte < sysdate - /*=moca_util.days(*/ 40 /*=)*/ and not exists (select 'x' from cntwrk where cnthdr.cntbat = cntwrk.cntbat and cntwrk.cntsts not in ('C', 'N')) and rownum<1000] }
